Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:31.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick...  {note, although these are flashbacks, the lines have been modified and re-dubbed, so consistency only needs to be reasonably kept}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive those who pretend to be from Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come join our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Council, Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots from Fairy Tail are at it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time they've destroyed half a port!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I quite like those bunch of fools, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed they are quite the fools, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they've assembled many \Nwizards of talent and ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you take the good with the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without those fools, this world would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon, Monkey, and Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go makin' trouble again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You half destroyed Harge-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That info about the salamander was a lie, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you some rumors that've been going around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something to get-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually made it into Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Natsu's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Gray Fullbuster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is capable at his work, but has a small...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...or rather, extreme habit of taking off his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna finish what we started, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray... Your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is Cana Alberona, \Nthe biggest drinker in all of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why all the men here have no class. {Cana's character tends to be plain-spoken. I understand the joke, but I think saying that they've got no class then drinking directly from a keg gets the point across.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put some clothes on and have at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All this crying and whining before noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Elfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll solve any kind of job with only his fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hyper-muscled wizard. {Super Physique makes it sound like that is the name of his magic, when in fact, he uses Take Over Magic described below}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, then talk with your fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's actually encouraging them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's already out for the count! {honorable death}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how noisy it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Loke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's high up on the list of "Most Eligible Wizards."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna mix it up, just for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this guy just went off my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, what's with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there not a single serious wizard in the joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a newcomer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirajane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is Mirajane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A wizard that does photo spreads \Nin the Weekly Sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She currently is an employee at Fairy Tail. {edit: The fact that she doesn't do jobs as a wizard becomes important later}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you sure it's okay not to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirajane-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, would you be so kind as to lend me your under-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These indelicate oafs causing you trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men talk with their fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's being so loud! I can't relax and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough out of all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What troublemakers you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:49.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna fight with magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:53.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were here, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's scared stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mi-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new recruit, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to have you on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, if you're the master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, this is Fairy Tail's \NGuild Master, Makarov-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone and done it again, rascals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all this paperwork the council sent me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The council.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:08:00.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}The Place from Before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization that manages \Nall the different Wizard's Guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you fools do is make the council angry at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw the council!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is an unreasonable power, \Nbut it is born from reason! {edit: I got tripped up reading this, so I did my best to clean it up}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not some miraculous ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the combination of the spirit that flows withing us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,with the spirit that flows within nature \Nitself, incarnated into physical form!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a strong mind and focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, magic is the pouring out of ones entire soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One cannot progress in the way of magic by being \Nmindful of the watchful eye from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be not afraid of those fools on the council!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And follow the path you believe in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:57.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a Fairy Tail wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with this, you're now a member of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got Fairy Tail's mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did? That's nice, Luigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the request board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards can choose whatever jobs they \Nlike from the requests posted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do one with a big reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, 160,000 jewel for subduing some thieves! {using subdue since that's what was written on the board}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't my dad come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting annoying, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the son of a wizard, then believe \Nin him and wait patiently at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he'd be back in three days, \Nand he hasn't come home for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a job at Mt. Hakobe, if I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that far away! Go out and look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your old man is a wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there ain't a wizard in this guild \Nwho can't take care of himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and drink some milk or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His words were harsh, \Nbut the master is actually worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu, don't break the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to save Macao, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why he's still such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All this is gonna do is hurt Macao's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:46.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can decide what someone \Nelse should do with their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is just like Romeo-kun, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened with Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the wizards at Fairy Tail carry something with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A scar, or pain... or suffering... {edit: The fact that all Fairy Tail wizards are damaged also becomes significant later}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you really can't handle transportation, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much to pity you for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's father left and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:41.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not his real father, \Nbut the parent who raised him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu was raised by a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was found by that dragon \Nin the forest when he was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:12:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it taught him how to read and \Neducated him, and taught him magic. {edit: "He taught him" gets me tripped up reading the subtitles. I think it's okay for Mirajane to call a dragon "it" Besides, although I think the dragon is male, I'm not absolutely sure.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, one day, it vanished, and Natsu couldn't find it. {edit: One interpretation was that the dragon became invisible. Not unreasonable for this world. I hope this wording clears it up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's Igneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is looking forward to \Nmeeting Igneel again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of cute of him, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we can't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I know it's a mountain and all, but it's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something not right about this blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for wearing such thin clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see you wearing a parka, either! {non-literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your muffler!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:58.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Clock, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Horologium!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She says "I'll be in here."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She says "What job did \NMacao-san come here to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know and tagged along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was subduing a vicious monster, a Vulcan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She says "I want to go home."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I say "Go right ahead."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Vulcan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A human woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who cares? Now, rescue me!" she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Near the peak of Mt. Hakobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why'd this have to happen to me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"And what's with this monkey... He's way too hyper!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Horologium! Don't disappear on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time. Fare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want an extension! An extension!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Macao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he incapable of making a normal entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, monkey! Where's Macao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking about Macao, a human man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Where are you hiding him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already decided the monkey's hiding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think it's getting through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need men! I like women!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman, woman, woman, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay you pervy monkey, get a load of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Golden Bull, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cow? {edit: ushi means both, and cow is just funnier -- what do you think?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:12.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus is the most powerful of all the \NCelestial spirits I have contracts with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, your body always does {\i1}you{\i0} good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be any moo-re lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he's a perv, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you take my woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your{\i0} woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have no moo-re of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampage! {can't think of a way to work in the moo pun here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty useless, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't there more monsters now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an ally, you dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait... How were you saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle transportation, but \NI guess Happy is no problem, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy isn't transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy is my partner.  You're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Fairy Tail are my friends and allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:37.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man and Mira, and even those \Nannoying jerks Gray and Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy and Lucy and everyone are all my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I'm gonna bring Macao back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work against fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Taurus' ax!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-wucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do then the ax will disappear too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's melting the ax... with his body heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.22,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}And he's eating it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to ask that \Nmonkey where Macao-san is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's him? Wasn't he a pervy \Nmonkey just a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vulcan must have done a Take Over. {edit: this comes back later, but Take Over is a type of magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic to occupy someone's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vulcans are monsters that live by stealing \Nhuman bodies and taking them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he put up a serious fight \Nbefore he was taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo's waitin' for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I defeated 19 of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got taken over by the 20th one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe myself, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't show my face to Romeo like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great defeating that many!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:19.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... There's more than one of those monkeys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was doing a job like that by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get you home. Romeo's waiting for you.  {non-literal for second half... works better in english methinks}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't match up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you grinning about, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull out your whiskers, cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail wizard's ain't nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just a bunch of cowards \Nwho spend all their time drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to become knights when we grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards are all a bunch of drunks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, go do a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay... I'm the son of a wizard, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time those bullies try and \Npick on you, tell them this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can your old man defeat 19 monsters, huh?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you too, Lucy! {ditto above}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:00.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,July 4th.  Sunny, then a blizzard, then sunny once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail might be one crazy messed up guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fun, and warm hearted, and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:12.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just be starting out as a wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I love this guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, my first gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I handle it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do fine, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:04.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard all about your adventures the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:10.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you defeated some guerrilla mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Natsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:13.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got it all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.56,0:24:17.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Infiltrate the Everlue Mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of job did you take, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.62,0:24:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
